_sText:
This map is the remastered version of trikz_dual which was posted months ago.

All the levels were retextured with shining textures and improved to do the map as fast as possible.

There are only 4 spawns (2 per team).

This map was made for sv_airaccelerate 10 and can be easily used as tournament map.

The map is composed of many levels which are 1 flashboost, 4 stackboosts, 2 runboost, 1 surf + bhop (made for aa10), 1 skyjump, 1 xc, and 3 little bhops.

Good Luck & Have Fun :D


PS: I added to the download .zip trikz_dual_1team, the training version of the map which contains 24 spawns CT.
